video.title: Oh No! It's an Alien Invasion
video.synopsis: Nate and his Super Wicked Extreme Emergency Team --  S.W.E.E.T. -- take on alien invaders who have captured all the world's grownups.

episodes.synopsis: Members of SWEET discover they're growing stupid, so it's a great time to start a school; SWEET members are in disguise to infiltrate the Brainlings.
episodes.title: Bak 2 Skool / Operation Dress-Up

episodes.synopsis: The boys of SWEET try everything to get into the girls' new secret club; the team discovers a gaseous solution to the Swell Mart's power-loss problem.
episodes.title: No Boys (or Aliens) Allowed / Go-Farts

episodes.synopsis: The world's top pop singer from before the invasion announces a concert; Louis's new robots, designed to clean the Swell Mart, annoy the rest of SWEET.
episodes.title: Pop Goes the Brainling / Robofolks

episodes.synopsis: Emperor Brainlius III threatens the city's toilets with his crazed flushing; SWEET tries to reverse the effects when Shakes is zapped by an aging ray.
episodes.title: The Royal Flush / The 'Stache

episodes.synopsis: Lily announces her own mission to save her parents with a cardboard spaceship; SWEET gets nervous when Shakes's new crush is on a lady Brainling.
episodes.title: Space Ramp / My Fair Ladyling

episodes.synopsis: The team decides to make a movie; Emperor Brainlius throws a party so loud that the Earth itself may be in danger.
episodes.title: Makin' Movie / Turn It Down

episodes.synopsis: Louis creates a superhero alter ego so he can save the world like SWEET; Scoop learns that the Swell Mart is in danger, but no one believes her.
episodes.title: The Spandexter / Scoop's Scoop

episodes.synopsis: Briiian creates Super Jumbo Ninja, a Brainling rival to Jumbo Ninja; Nate gets mistaken for Emperor Brainlius III at a costume party.
episodes.title: Super Jumbo Ninja /  Emperor for a Day

episodes.synopsis: The members of SWEET get the flu and decide to share it with the Brainlings; Emperor Brainlius III hires Shakes to be his personal chef.
episodes.title: Brainflu / Chef Shakes

episodes.synopsis: SWEET and the Brainlings compete at figure skating; Emperor Brainlius III's parade route runs right through the Swell Mart.
episodes.title: Brainlings on Ice /  Brainlings on Parade

episodes.synopsis: SWEET encounters an elderly ghost haunting the Swell Mart; the team must save the Swell Mart from attacking werevambies.
episodes.title: Grampa Ghost / Night of the Werevambies

episodes.synopsis: Briiian turns a pet unicorn into an unstoppable machine of destruction; the members of SWEET rescue their first adult from the Brainlings.
episodes.title: Unitron / Dan the Man

episodes.synopsis: Lily makes friends with Gorthax, Emperor Brainlius III's favorite pet; the members of SWEET celebrate Switcheroo Day by trading places.
episodes.title: Free Gorthax /  The Switcheroo

episodes.synopsis: SWEET has trouble understanding Jumbo Ninja when he runs out of his favorite cereal; a robot musician joins Nate's band.
episodes.title: Lord of the Loops  / Harmoniator

episodes.synopsis: A single lost shoe leads Nate and Dan the Man to a secret military base; Nate finds himself trapped in a bunker with Emperor Brainlius III.
episodes.title: Raiders of the Lost and Found / Aliens in the Bunker

episodes.synopsis: SWEET tries to stop Emperor Brainlius III from breaking every human record; Nate becomes a wrestling hero with the help of an old championship belt.
episodes.title: The Brainling Book of Records / The Champ Is Here

episodes.synopsis: A bounty hunter is dispatched to round up SWEET; the members of SWEET create an infomercial designed to separate Emperor Brainlius III from his money.
episodes.title: Flex Hammerstone – Bounty Hunter /  Informer-cial

episodes.synopsis: A raucous party lures Mr. Crash to Earth, alarming the Brainlings; SWEET teams up with extreme new friends Flea and Tick to take back a playground.
episodes.title: Calling Mr. Crash /  Lord of the Fleas

episodes.synopsis: A group of prisoners attempts to break out of a Brainling prison; Nate seems to be the biggest star in Scoop's new blooper compilation.
episodes.title: The Great Escape / Scoop's World

episodes.synopsis: SWEET must rescue Shakes when he's zapped into the Brainternet; Turret decides to leave SWEET for a rival group, YEAH.
episodes.title: Going Viral / Team Turret

episodes.synopsis: Shakes and Nate get covered in perfume that the Brainlings love; Louis lands in an alternate universe with good Brainlings and a bad SWEET team.
episodes.title: Smell Mart /  Oh Yes!

episodes.synopsis: The team dresses Jumbo Ninja as Santa Claus to try to save Christmas; Shakes, Scoop and Louis must save the city from a Brainling device.
episodes.title: Ho Oh No! / Countdown to Terror

episodes.synopsis: SWEET tries to help put Scoop's new painting into an art gallery; no one knows who to trust when SWEET's spaceship vanishes.
episodes.title: Artsy Fartsy / Joy Ride

episodes.synopsis: The Brainlings capture SWEET and force them to participate in the Plunger Games; SWEET uses sabotage to turn the Brainlings into "Muffings."
episodes.title: The Plunger Games / Mufflings

episodes.synopsis: A humongous ball of trash from space threatens the Earth; Briiian wears Emperor Brainlius III's crown as ruler for a day.
episodes.title: Space Trash / The King and Bri

episodes.synopsis: Briiian finally uncovers the location of SWEET's secret base; SWEET launches an attack on the Flying Swell Mart.
episodes.title: Brian Mart I /  Brian Mart II

episodes.synopsis: Briiian hires a new assistant, unaware that it's Nate in disguise; Lily's hiccups turn out to be an effective offensive weapon against the Brainlings.
episodes.title: The Assistant / Hiccups

episodes.synopsis: When SWEET holds annual elections, Emperor Brainlius III runs for the top job; Shakes believes he's an action hero.
episodes.title: In Brain We Trust / The Shakedown

episodes.synopsis: Scoop is able to predict the future after eating a carton of expired yogurt; Lily is made Nate's bodyguard.
episodes.title: The Future Is Now / The Boogieguard

episodes.synopsis: Multiple Emperor Brainlius IIIs start turning up when the Brainlings discover cloning technology; Briiian discovers the secrets in Turret's journal.
episodes.title: Brainlius III-VI-V / Diary Drama

episodes.synopsis: Jumbo Ninja becomes a green blur when he's hit with a speed ray; Emperor Brainlius III develops a crush on a robot.
episodes.title: The Green Blur / Head of the Household

episodes.synopsis: Briiian goes on trial before the members of SWEET; Louis and Scoop find themselves lost in the suburban jungle.
episodes.title: Food Court / Lost in the Hood

episodes.synopsis: Nate concocts a phony alien invasion to turn the tables on the Brainlings; the members of SWEET enter Emperor Brainlius III's dreams.
episodes.title: Oh No It's Another Alien Invasion / Brainception

episodes.synopsis: SWEET doesn't know how to react when Nate befriends a Brainling; Lily and Turret go on patrol as Swell Mart mall cops.
episodes.title: Brain Bros / Swell Mart PD

episodes.synopsis: SWEET celebrates Lily's birthday; the Brainlings and the members of SWEET compete to see who has the cutest pet.
episodes.title: Lily’s B-Day / Just Goes to (Pet) Show

episodes.synopsis: Emperor Brainlius III starts a new dance sensation; Lily takes on Emperor Brainlius III in a bicycle race.
episodes.title: Dance Craze / Bike Psyche

episodes.synopsis: The members of SWEET have trouble deciding on the group's new theme song; the Brainlings trap Dash and Nate on a date.
episodes.title: Bandemonium / Dash Date

episodes.synopsis: The members of SWEET discover the importance of toothpaste; SWEET crashes the opening night of Emperor Brainlius III's new musical.
episodes.title: Stink Mouth / Brainlius the Musical

episodes.synopsis: Emperor Brainlius III is under the delusion that he's a vampire; Nate and Lily are turned into ghosts themselves when Grandpa Ghost returns.
episodes.title: Fangs but No Fangs / Grandpa Ghost II

episodes.synopsis: The members of SWEET and YEAH team up to attack the Brainlings; Nate believes he knows where Emperor Brainlius III is keeping the Earth's adults.
episodes.title: S.W.E.E.T. Swap / The Belly Bag
